overview: There's shakin', quakin' and plenty of booty to be enjoyed when the perky gals from Aloha High School shimmy their groove things in this red-hot sequel to The Cheerleaders. Rainbeaux Smith (from the first film) is back ... and pregnant!
tagline: It's High School the Way We Remember It ... Although It Never Happened Quite Like This!
title: Revenge of the Cheerleaders
